'''环球足球奖'''（Globe Soccer Awards或Dubai d'Ors）是为表彰优秀的[[足球运动员|足球运动员]]而设立的年度奖项。頒獎儀式由席尔瓦国际投资公司（Silva International Investments）<ref name="prnewswireref-">{{Cite web|title=Silva International Investments Acquires Stake in Globe Soccer|url=https://www.prnewswire.com/in/news-releases/silva-international-investments-acquires-stake-in-globe-soccer-666738373.html|access-date=2020-12-28|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227200046/https://www.prnewswire.com/in/news-releases/silva-international-investments-acquires-stake-in-globe-soccer-666738373.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、托马索・本多尼（Tommaso Bendoni ）<ref name="sportbusinessref-">{{Cite web|title=Special edition of the Dubai Globe Soccer Awards set to break new ground {{!}} SportBusiness|url=https://www.sportbusiness.com/2020/11/special-edition-of-the-dubai-globe-soccer-awards-set-to-break-new-ground/|access-date=2020-12-28|archive-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228113449/https://www.sportbusiness.com/2020/11/special-edition-of-the-dubai-globe-soccer-awards-set-to-break-new-ground/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和马尔代夫（Maldives）主席阿卜杜拉・贾比尔（Abdulla Jabir）/H.提马维斯希（H. Thimaaveshi ）共同組織。每年12月（2018年除外，當年的獎項拖延至2019年1月舉辦），主辦方在頒發环球足球奖時都会在[[迪拜|迪拜]]举办一場官方晚宴。在晚宴上，来自各大洲的主要足球名将都会出席颁奖典礼，许多电视网络也会直播晚宴现场。

